(2, 'PTE Long Course(Batch)', 'PTE 1 to 1 short course (On Campus)', '20', 4000.00, 'Basic', 20, '30', 'PEC-Education conduct special PTE preparation short course(Crash course) to the candidate who needs special care particularly not interested to attend in a PTE Academic batch. This course is a classroom based which is arranged at the PTE Academic centre in Mirpur, Dhaka, Bangladesh. The advantage of this course is flexible with timing according to the candidate’s availability. The duration of the course is 16 hours along with free study materials as well as PTE practice materials. 5 free mock tests will be provided along with scorecard and free assessment.', 'Video Conference', '2026-03-23 10:37:48');

