png?resize=768%2C417&amp;ssl=1 768w, https://i0.wp.com/pecpte.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/CIBEx-PEC-Course-Catalog-Oct.-02-2020.png?resize=20%2C11&amp;ssl=1 20w, https://i0.wp.com/pecpte.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/10/CIBEx-PEC-Course-Catalog-Oct.-02-2020.png?resize=600%2C326&amp;ssl=1 600w\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></div></figure></div></div></div></div></div></div></div>', '2026-03-23 09:14:20'),
(3, 'study aboard', '<div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6\" style=\"width: 600px; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: left; color: rgb(39, 48, 68); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\" style=\"padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; width: 600px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"vc_custom_heading text_align_left\"><h2 class=\"masterstudy-custom-title\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 38px; color: rgb(39, 48, 68); margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 36px; text-align: left;\">Benefits to Study Abroad</h2></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \" style=\"margin-bottom: 35px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(39, 48, 68); margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.2px; text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Opportunity to see the world.</strong></h4></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(39, 48, 68); margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.2px; text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\">To experience different styles of Education</strong></h4></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(39, 48, 68); margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.2px; text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Opportunity to witness a completely new way of life</strong></h4></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(39, 48, 68); margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.2px; text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Great chance of getting better career life.</strong></h4></li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><h4 style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 26px; color: rgb(39, 48, 68); margin-bottom: 0px; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: -0.2px; text-align: left;\"><strong style=\"font-weight: bold; margin-bottom: 0px;\">Make life long multinational friends.</strong></h4></li></ul></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-6\" style=\"width: 600px; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: left; color: rgb(39, 48, 68); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\" style=\"padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; width: 600px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"vc_custom_heading text_align_center\"><h2 class=\"masterstudy-custom-title\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 38px; color: rgb(39, 48, 68); margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 36px; text-align: center;\">Our Cooperation to study abroad</h2></div><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \" style=\"margin-bottom: 35px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px;\">PEC-Education has been helping students to study abroad with step by step procedures.<br style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">We try to assure your success be providing appropriate strategies. Moreover, we assist students without any kind of return or finance.</p><ul style=\"margin-bottom: 0px; padding-left: 20px;\"><li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\">Most of the time we connect with students by filling our visiting online /offline form.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\">For the second procedure, we operate face to face free counseling sessions with students to know about his interest.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\">Support for language proficiency tests like PTE Academic/IELTS with a special discount for our students.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\">The complete Application process to overseas universities with a special discount and sometimes free of cost of tuition fee for several universities in Canada and Australia.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\">We cooperate to arrange documents like SOP, Letter of Intent, etc.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\">&nbsp;Collect student’s admission offer letter and show the way of the visa process.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 8px;\">&nbsp;We guide to accomplish the other financial documents in a secure and trustworthy way.</li><li style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\">&nbsp;Appoint companion to enjoy your safe and sound journey to your destination.</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div>', '2026-03-23 10:42:52'),
(4, 'pte mock tests', '<div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\" style=\"margin-bottom: 35px; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; color: rgb(39, 48, 68); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-8\" style=\"width: 800px; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: left;\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\" style=\"padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; width: 800px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_single_image wpb_content_element vc_align_left\" style=\"margin-bottom: 35px; text-align: left;\"><h2 class=\"wpb_heading wpb_singleimage_heading\" style=\"font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-weight: 700; line-height: 38px; color: rgb(39, 48, 68); margin-bottom: 30px; font-size: 36px;\">PTE Mock Test</h2><figure class=\"wpb_wrapper vc_figure\" style=\"display: inline-block; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%;\"><a class=\"\" data-lightbox=\"lightbox[rel-4902-784036913]\" href=\"https://i0.wp.com/pecpte.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/PTE-Mock-Test.jpg?fit=1024%2C658&amp;ssl=1\" target=\"_self\" style=\"color: rgb(44, 117, 228); outline: 0px; transition: 0.25s; border: none; text-decoration: none !important;\"><img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"vc_single_image-img entered lazyloaded\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/pecpte.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/PTE-Mock-Test-700x600.jpg\" width=\"700\" height=\"600\" alt=\"PTE Mock Test\" title=\"PTE Mock Test\" data-lazy-src=\"https://i0.wp.com/pecpte.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/04/PTE-Mock-Test-700x600.jpg\" data-ll-status=\"loaded\" style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: top; max-width: 100%; height: auto;\"></a></figure></div></div></div></div><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-4\" style=\"width: 400px; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: left;\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\" style=\"padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; width: 400px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_inner vc_row-fluid\" style=\"margin-bottom: 35px; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px;\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-12\" style=\"width: 400px; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: left;\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\" style=\"padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; width: 400px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_btn3-container vc_btn3-center\" style=\"margin-bottom: 21.7391px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center;\"></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"vc_row wpb_row vc_row-fluid\" style=\"margin-bottom: 35px; margin-left: -15px; margin-right: -15px; color: rgb(39, 48, 68); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; text-align: justify;\"><div class=\"wpb_column vc_column_container vc_col-sm-8\" style=\"width: 800px; position: relative; min-height: 1px; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; float: left;\"><div class=\"vc_column-inner\" style=\"padding-left: 15px; padding-right: 15px; width: 800px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\"><div class=\"wpb_text_column wpb_content_element \" style=\"margin-bottom: 35px;\"><div class=\"wpb_wrapper\" style=\"margin-bottom: 0px;\"><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px;\">The candidate is requested to click the above button to sign in to our&nbsp;<a href=\"https://pecpte.com/product/pte-online-mock-test1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" style=\"color: rgb(44, 117, 228); transition: 0.25s; margin-bottom: 0px; text-decoration: none !important; outline: 0px !important;\">PTE Mock</a>&nbsp;tests platform which has been created only for you. Please put afterward your ID and Password which has given to you. Please note that this ID and password is confidential and never share with anyone.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 30px; margin-left: 0px;\">Our PTE Mock Tests are full length, duration of 2 hours, and completely online-based. These PTE mock tests can be attempted anytime from your home. The validity of our PTE Mock Tests will be for 3(Three) days only. Candidates need to have good quality Headphone and Mic. Internet bandwidth or speed is preferred at least 2 Mbps to get the uninterrupted services. Once the PTE Mock test is completed, the scorecard and assessment report will be delivered within 24 hours to the candidate’s email.</p><p style=\"margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; margin-left: 0px;\">If you face any difficulties logging in, do not hesitate to contact our customer care.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div>', '2026-03-23 10:43:22');
